    "title": "Smart Metrolac",
    "description": "An IoT-based measurement system designed to replace traditional glass metrolacs with precision gravimetric sensing. By integrating real-time spoilage detection and cloud-based data tracking, we provide a transparent, fraud-resistant solution for the Sri Lankan rubber industry, ensuring fair trade for farmers and accuracy for industrial collectors.",
